Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.30,0:00:30.23,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When I was just sixteen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.75,0:00:32.95,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I had a car that was lean and mean~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.73,0:00:35.93,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Put Dashie in my window
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.15,0:00:39.09,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Was the coolest thing I'd seen
