Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.07,0:00:54.13,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But I had my group of friends~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.79,0:00:57.24,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Who would defend me to the end~~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.13,0:01:01.72,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And we picked up every piece and tried
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.94,0:01:03.91,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To make her whole again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.84,0:01:08.60,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,'Cause toge~ther we can do it
