Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.72,0:01:14.26,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Though everypony loves~ to shun us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.83,0:01:16.85,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Together we stand proud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.11,0:01:19.92,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Hoof in hoof we all will weather
